      <title>欧盟对特朗普的答案可能涉及大型技术的数据使用，法国说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-05/eu-answer-to-trump-may-involve-data-use-by-big-tech-france-says</link>
