      <title>关税stoke担心挂债会返回</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-05/tariffs-stoke-fears-that-hung-debt-will-return-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杠杆融资的交易已经停滞不前，市场已被颠覆，这增加了银行可能再次被他们承诺收购的债务所困扰的可能性。]]></description>
